143
00:09:09,607 --> 00:09:11,280
She kept busting me.

144
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:13,894
The drug's like our secret affair, right?

145
00:09:13,894 --> 00:09:17,907
The lies catch up with us, 'cause we ain't 
nearly as smart as we think we are.

146
00:09:17,907 --> 00:09:19,846
Jasmine was my dream girl, too.

147
00:09:19,846 --> 00:09:21,303
How so?

148
00:09:21,303 --> 00:09:22,963
I don't know.

149
00:09:23,987 --> 00:09:26,155
She was hot.

150
00:09:26,454 --> 00:09:28,686
What about you, Joseph?

151
00:09:28,686 --> 00:09:30,584
Who's your dream girl?

152
00:09:30,584 --> 00:09:32,812
I don't have a lot of time
for relationships right now.

153
00:09:32,812 --> 00:09:35,171
I got my hands full with you punks.

154
00:09:35,171 --> 00:09:38,672
Oh, must be something
that turns up your temperature.

155
00:09:39,055 --> 00:09:44,197
Guess it would be someone smart, 
as passionate about her work as I am,

156
00:09:44,197 --> 00:09:47,443
and not allergic to cats.

157
00:09:49,367 --> 00:09:52,139
How about you, Corey?

158
00:09:53,282 --> 00:09:55,437
Someone fine.

159
00:09:55,437 --> 00:09:57,644
You know, who dresses nice.

160
00:09:57,644 --> 00:10:00,940
Someone who gives a damn about me.

161
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:03,692
See, that's an important step, Corey.

162
00:10:03,692 --> 00:10:06,490
'Cause you're right,
