163
00:10:06,490 --> 00:10:09,559
I mean, you all do.

164
00:10:09,559 --> 00:10:11,772
I get your subliminal message, Joseph.

165
00:10:11,772 --> 00:10:14,438
- What message?
- Just because I'm allergic to cats,

166
00:10:14,438 --> 00:10:17,669
