185
00:12:04,085 --> 00:12:07,905
Take us back to a year ago,
back when you were in a bad way.

186
00:12:07,905 --> 00:12:09,863
You told Joseph Shaw you loved him

187
00:12:09,863 --> 00:12:13,044
