190
00:12:19,734 --> 00:12:21,708
Shot by me?
No, you're wrong.

191
00:12:21,708 --> 00:12:23,713
That so?

192
00:12:24,608 --> 00:12:28,672
You know how...
if a person is drowning,

193
00:12:28,672 --> 00:12:32,478
