the person who's rescuing them?

194
00:12:32,478 --> 00:12:34,176
Sure.

195
00:12:34,176 --> 00:12:36,910
Joseph was the person who'd rescue you.

196
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:39,666
Saying that put him in harm's way?

197
00:12:41,406 --> 00:12:46,897
- You gonna say by who?
- Oh, but it's so sad. / Crystal.

198
00:12:47,619 --> 00:12:50,379
Joseph's foster brother.

199
00:12:50,379 --> 00:12:52,158
He stopped by one time

200
