Joseph's family is as bad as mine."

201
00:12:56,634 --> 00:12:59,034
Which is bad.

202
00:13:00,811 --> 00:13:04,164
Every guy who's ever liked me...

203
00:13:04,164 --> 00:13:07,521
dies including Orlando.

204
00:13:08,867 --> 00:13:11,384
- Wilder, what are you doing here?
- Hey, bro. / Hi.

205
00:13:11,384 --> 00:13:12,845
Crystal, can you step out for a minute?

206
00:13:12,845 --> 00:13:14,846
No, no. I'll be real quick.

207
00:13:14,846 --> 00:13:16,950
Landlord's screwing me.
Wants a deposit.

208
00:13:16,950 --> 00:13:18,971
I've given you my last dime.

209
00:13:18,971 --> 00:13:20,940
I'm gonna leave.

210
00:13:20,940 --> 00:13:23,874
