all right? Not this.

213
00:13:30,070 --> 00:13:33,911
Look, I know she made you
feel like you're nothing.

214
00:13:33,911 --> 00:13:36,391
But you're not.

215
00:13:36,391 --> 00:13:38,337
You're not, man.

216
00:13:38,337 --> 00:13:42,477
Joe wants to make everybody
perfect, like him.

217
00:13:43,061 --> 00:13:45,569
No, thanks.

218
00:13:45,569 --> 00:13:47,655
See you.

219
00:13:56,511 --> 00:13:58,305
Stop!

220
00:13:59,014 --> 00:14:01,562
Get out!

221
00:14:08,065 --> 00:14:12,864
Wilder's mom, Joseph's foster mom...

222
00:14:12,864 --> 00:14:17,948
she would, like, not let them eat,
but she'd, like, stuff her face.

223
00:14:17,948 --> 00:14:19,415
