602
00:39:37,236 --> 00:39:40,370
We can be happy.

603
00:39:40,370 --> 00:39:43,996
'Cause that's what Tom would want.

604
00:39:47,855 --> 00:39:53,633
I just miss him, Teddy.
I do.

